           <h2>MISSION STATEMENT</h2>
           <p>The mission statement of Deaf Advocates for Lives of Integrity without Violence through Empowerment (DeafALIVE) is:</p>
           <p><em>Our mission is to end Domestic and sexual violence through ASL (American Sign Language).</em></p>
           <h2>ORGANIZATION GOALS</h2>
           <p>Across Indiana, the overall organization goals of DeafALIVE are to:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-10 mb-10">
                <li>Provide and promote Domestic Violence/Sexual Awareness through community outreach</li>
                <li>Provide resources and empowerment to community members, partners, and survivors to support the needs of Deaf and hard of hearing survivors</li>
